Start
Initialize ESP32
Initialize Soil Moisture Sensor
Initialize LDR Sensor
Initialize Relay (Pump)
Initialize Push Button
Initialize LCD
Connect to Wi-Fi
Loop
Read Soil Moisture Value
Read LDR Value
If Manual Button is Pressed
    Turn Pump ON
    Wait 5 Minutes
    Turn Pump OFF
Else
  If Soil is Dry
 If LDR Detects Rain (Low Light)
            Pump OFF
   Else
            Pump ON
        End If
   Else
        Pump OFF
    End If
End If
Display Moisture Percentage
Display Pump Status
Display Last Watered Time
Upload Data to Google Sheets
Wait 30 Minutes
Repeat
